      <title>美国打击胡塞武装并指责伊拉克组织对约旦无人机袭击负责</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/us-strikes-houthis-blames-islamic-resistance-in-iraq-for-jordan-drone-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着以色列与哈马斯战争的余波继续扰乱该地区，美国对也门胡塞武装目标发动了两次单独袭击，并拦截了伊朗支持的胡塞组织发射的一枚导弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/us-strikes-houthis-blames-islamic-resistance-in-iraq-for-jordan-drone-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 07:06:04 GMT</pubDate>
